            <title><![CDATA[Nintendo Patent Application Seems To Confirm Switch 2 Joy-Con Feature]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-patent-application-seems-to-confirm-switch-2-joy-con-feature/1100-6529310/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
